listings.description: A substantial five bedroom detached residence that will immediately impress with its spacious rooms, living spaces and elegant, beautifully appointed interior throughout. The property boasts five bedrooms, four bathrooms along with a wonderful kitchen with additional breakfast room.

Offering premium living on a highly desirable road and showcasing an ultra-contemporary design, this stunning detached residence offers 2137 sq. Ft of living space and is beautifully presented with spacious, light-filled interiors, solid oak flooring throughout, a large, landscaped rear garden and extensive off-street parking.

Ideally positioned for excellent transport links, local amenities and highly regarded schools, this immaculately presented four bedroom home is situated in a sought-after and convenient location, perfect for the modern-day family.

Orchard Property Services are delighted to present this exceptionally well presented, skilfully designed and extended four bedroom modern spacious residence, offering unrivalled and contemporary living space having undergone a sympathetic, yet high specification renovation and being set on a prestigious private road in the ever popular North Ruislip.

With stylish interiors and a choice of generous living areas, this commanding four/five bedroom residence will impress those seeking space, luxury and a convenient address, it promises a superior family lifestyle. It has been modernised offering a host of high specification which include a bespoke kitchen and wood flooring in certain rooms.

This delightful three bedroom detached bungalow offers spacious, light-filled interiors throughout and is situated in a sought after location, close to the areas vast array of amenities, school and transport links. The property also has the added benefit of a separate annex.

Situated in a sought after and convenient location is this immaculately presented three bedroom detached family house on Monarchs Way, Ruislip. Ideally positioned close to Ruislip High Street with highly regarded Junior and Secondary Schools nearby.

A unique four bedroom detached family home set on this popular residential side road in the heart of Ruislip, with easy access to Ruislip high street and close by to Ruislip Woods. Features include a complete upper chain, nearly 1,500 sq ft living accommodation with further potential to extend STPP, four bedrooms, garage and large private rear garden.

This 1930's built end of terrace house has been extended to the side and rear, creating much larger than average accommodation. There is driveway parking, secluded rear garden, three bedrooms on the first floor and a large bedroom with en-suite on the ground floor. Local shops and schools are within a short walk and the central line station is also easily accessible.

Situated in arguably one of the most sought after roads in the local area is this larger than average semi-detached family home. The property requires modernisation and is being sold with no chain; the buyer of this house has an opportunity to extend it further to create a fantastic family home. Ruislip & Ruislip Manor stations are within easy reach, as are a number of well-regarded local schools.

Offered to the market in good condition is this spacious four bedroom semi detached family home, with its own drive way and detached garage, located in Ruislip. Purplebricks recommend a prompt viewing.

A well proportioned four bedroom semi-detached home set in this highly convenient location. Having already been improved upon by its current owners, the property briefly comprises: Through lounge/dining room, fitted kitchen, four good size bedrooms and bathroom suite. The property benefits include: Conservatory, downstairs cloakroom, en suite shower room, rear garden, summerhouse, storage garage and own driveway for approximately two vehicles.
